{
  "stem": "26728.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 22.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, this is the first I had ever heard of a-- of a gas chamber, other than the ones that we read about in the States.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, and I don't think I knew much about them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyhow, the curiosity was not so much for me, you know, as it-- as it was from this other fellow who-- who decided there's no way that that could be a shower, because it said 'shower' on the sign.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were shower heads inside, you know, coming out of the wall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so, you know, 25 or 30 people could take a shower at the same time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but he fooled around with it and he could not find any plumbing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's what-- he said to me, there's no way-- and we were having a cigarette or something-- there's no way that-- that you could take a shower in there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even though they had already told us it was a gas chamber, we figure that what they turned the valve someplace and the gas came out of these shower heads.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's what my-- my perception was that was not it at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took-- there were chutes, uh, in the ceiling, in the roof of the building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were, say, like-- say like a post or a sieve-like sheet metal post that came from outside to inside with holes, perforations-- and the-- they would-- and there probably four or five, and I don't remember now.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There is a picture somewhere in there-- of even seeing these things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they-- but they were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what they-- the way this guy had talked to some of the inmates, and-- and eventually I got to talk to this one guy.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
